Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:51.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是十丸院先生介绍而来的阿藤勇马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:51.23,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：发音同「一瞬之间」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:52.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:54.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好青年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十丸院先生意外的挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:01.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那么在这儿画上观叶植物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:02.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,责编最重要的技能之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,便是能想方设法介绍来优秀的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:12.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可不认为那个十丸院能找到什么靠谱的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:14.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请过目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  已经画好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:18.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很出色啊
