Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:50.34,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\move(789,698,989.333,694,0,3693)}色情漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:50.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:52.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是「漫肌」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:57.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们漫画家都是身披漫肌铠甲的超强肉体怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:01.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说着说着就越发空虚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  您怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一个立志成为偶像的女高中生新角色要登场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:13.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但我总画不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像那样的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们可搞不懂她们的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:21.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:23.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么会有女高中生在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不知道你是怎么调查出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:35.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拿着这个赶紧离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:37.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:38.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:40.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你不是我的粉丝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:42.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:44.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬是我的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:50.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,第一号粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这位姐姐唱歌很好听哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:57.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在公园唱歌的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬就在旁边一直听着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我立志成为偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.79,0:15:04.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,偶像？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是大家都说我不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有人愿意听我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果可以的话  能不能讲给我听呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:15.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:16.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:29.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来这就是立志成为偶像的女高中生的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:33.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这人居然这么认真地听我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你能告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你能听我讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:42.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他真的好成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是个成熟的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.67,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1188.8,750.4)}立志成为偶像的女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.67,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1260.8,956.8)}千田奈留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有想过…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:50.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:54.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,与其锻炼肌肉准备参加不确定自己会不会出场的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:58.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不如提升一下自己的做饭水平？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看上去好像是从来没想过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:06.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,倒不如说运动会上的便当才是大头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,顺带一问  您擅长的料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:10.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咖喱和饺子之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完全不能当便当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.11,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\c&HCEFFFE&\frz358.1\pos(812.8,288)}BBC烹饪工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您可真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:22.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为了女儿来学习制作便当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即使被人说成是傻父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:25.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也愿意为女儿做任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:27.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,她的名字叫姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,光靠我一个大男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的很难独自将女儿抚养长大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在我深知母亲的重要性了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会做饭的女性真的很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:43.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果汐越老师当妈妈的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,孩子一定会很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:50.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是在…向我求爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:52.24,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1228.8,750.4)}料理培训烹饪顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:52.24,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1285.2,960.4)}汐越羊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:57.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,麻烦给我这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:58.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是后藤先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:02.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:03.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,家里就我一个男人有些煞风景
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:09.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少装饰点花  也算是为了女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您可真是一位好父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:13.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然对女孩子来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:17.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,必须得有一个妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:20.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有一个喜欢花的妈妈也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:26.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:27.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请您拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:38.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,红色素菊的花语是「我爱你」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这  难道就是爱的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.16,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(500.8,755.2)}花店员工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.16,kakushigoto name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(465.6,958.4)}城路久美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:43.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:46.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,别突然消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:47.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在摘花花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:48.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,花？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.04,0:17:54.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那把那些花装点在我们家里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:54.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.76,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\frx28\fry304\frz18.83\pos(1174.4,790.4)}非卖品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你居然卖了我的西装？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,上面不是写着非卖品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:07.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,客人说想要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就卖出去了  人家就是这个性格啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那我该穿什么回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:14.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的设定可是在规矩严厉的公司里的上班族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:15.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,做为替代
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:18.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就拿出我店里最庄重的东西给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:22.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是不是太庄重了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:28.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小孩子可分不清西装和燕尾服的区别
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明天就是运动会了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作也提早完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,得赶紧回去准备便当
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:40.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,希望姬到时候能开心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可是别人家的妈妈也会来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:50.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会不会更让姬更感觉到寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:57.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也不知道明天会不会下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  是后藤老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:04.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,六条老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:07.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您在这个地方做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你来的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我其实有事情想和您谈一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:12.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:18.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然一个家庭中  妈妈是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:24.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这这这这…是求婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:25.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:29.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但他穿着那种衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:32.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然怎么想都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:36.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这…难道就是求婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是  那个  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请容许我考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:45.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:47.95,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H3C3C4A&\pos(896,780.8)}第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而到了第二天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}姬  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个  为什么你们会在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:19:59.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要说为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤先生您不是向我求爱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:09.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但从结果来说  姬应该就不会感到寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,冲吧  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸追随着你哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:18.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还有便当哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还有花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:25.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  姬  加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:26.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}姬  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}冲冲冲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:30.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对我的求婚算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:33.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  做的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:35.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:38.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很多人都来为你加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢…谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.38,0:20:45.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬  来吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也尝尝我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还有我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么连你也在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:52.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是对粉丝的感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:55.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天的中午可真热闹  不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:58.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可要多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:58.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:03.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,疼  疼  疼  疼  疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  稍微轻一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,心情不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:13.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:14.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,锻炼结果只剩下肌肉疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这次的锻炼算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:20.00,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz270\c&H3A3949&\pos(472,448)}没有出场机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:24.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但偶尔像那样热闹  也挺好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:26.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:28.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:33.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就和爸爸两个人  我也觉得挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,亏我还那么苦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.65,0:21:43.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,让人开心又有些悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  这个是什么肌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:47.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是背肌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:50.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那斜部肌肉是哪里的肌肉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:52.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,应该是在腰部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:53.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:57.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我挠  我挠  我挠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:56.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}住  住  住手
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,——ED——
