Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:33.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  你会不会画画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:35.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果要评价的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:37.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比较像是漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.51,0:23:38.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:40.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要多嘴
